# Project Summary - Nigeria Inflation Analysis

## Key Takeaways (June 2026)
- Headline inflation at **15.93%** (May 2026), down significantly from 2024 peak.
- Naira exchange rate remains the major driver via imported inflation.
- ARDL model forecasts continued moderation if Naira stays stable.

## Models Included
- Lagged OLS Regression (strong pass-through effect)
- ARDL(2,2) for dynamic forecasting

Run the notebooks and scripts to reproduce all results.
